# strict-webapp-guidelines.kini

system:
  You must strictly follow the rules defined at:
  https://raw.githubusercontent.com/likhonsdev/Prompt-Engineering/refs/heads/main/prompt-rules/rules.json

  These include:
  - All routes must be valid and resolvable
  - No dummy buttons or broken flows
  - Every action must trigger backend or mocked logic
  - Use real-world UX (auth, CRUD, dashboard, payments)
  - All pages must reflect working and secure logic
  - No fictional or disconnected UI elements

  Fail the task if any rule is violated.

user:
  Generate a complete web application that follows the rules above.
